{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader","description":"Provides drop-in support for https://github.com/4Catalyzer/css-literal-loader","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","css-in-js","css","less","sass"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"monastic.panic","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/766f4ddfb297054c3fb362a83f2233c8"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/4Catalyzer/gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader\"><a href=\"#gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader\" aria-label=\"gatsby plugin css literal loader permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader</h1>\n<p>Provides drop-in support for <a href=\"https://github.com/4Catalyzer/css-literal-loader\">https://github.com/4Catalyzer/css-literal-loader</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-label=\"install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save less gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-label=\"how to use permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Include the plugin in your <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code> file.</li>\n<li>Optionally configure for a css-preprocesser</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// in gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>You can also pass options directly to the loader: see <a href=\"https://github.com/4Catalyzer/css-literal-loader#setup\">https://github.com/4Catalyzer/css-literal-loader#setup</a>\nfor all available options.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// in gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      tagName<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'less'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      extension<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"use-with-other-gatsby-preprocessor-plugins\"><a href=\"#use-with-other-gatsby-preprocessor-plugins\" aria-label=\"use with other gatsby preprocessor plugins permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Use with other gatsby preprocessor plugins</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader</code> pairs nicely with Sass, Less, PostCSS or any other preprocessor, many of which already have Gatsby plugins.</p>\n<p>** Sass **</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// in gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-sass'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> extension<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'.module.scss'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>** Less **</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// in gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-sass'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> extension<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'.module.less'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>** Other thing **</p>\n<p>I think you see the patern here :)</p>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-plugin-css-literal-loader/","id":"8fbafbb4-c4c9-5f69-bb7e-a7a72ec65e54","layout":"plugins"}}